<br />
<br />2) Is CHRRAM available for mapper 0 ROMs aswell?
<br />
<br />3) When powering up a "real" NES cartridge, RAM will contain garbage (as I've heard), how will this work with PowerPak? Do you clear the RAM before the user starts a ROM? Perhaps not that important but I think it's interesting.
